{
  "info": {
    "name": "Redemptions API",
    "description": "Prize redemption and voucher management endpoints\n\n**Base URL**: `{{base_url}}`\n\n**Auth**: Bearer token in `Authorization` header (from Auth0)\n\n**Features**:\n- Individual prize redemption\n- Admin voucher distribution (single user)\n- Admin bulk voucher distribution\n- User redemption history",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Admin - Send Single Voucher",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{auth_token}}",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"clh1234567890abcdefghijk\",\n  \"email\": \"user@company.com\",\n  \"prizeId\": \"clh9876543210zyxwvutsrqp\",\n  \"customAmount\": 50.00\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/admin/redemptions/send-to-user",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "admin",
            "redemptions",
            "send-to-user"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Send a single voucher to a user via email\n\n**Required Permissions**: `vouchers:send_to_users`\n\n**Request Body**:\n- `userId` (string): CUID of the target user\n- `email` (string): Email must match user's registered email\n- `prizeId` (string): CUID of a voucher prize\n- `customAmount` (number): Amount must be within voucher's minValue/maxValue range\n\n**Note**: Campaign ID is set to a fixed constant on the server side.\n\n**Response**: 202 Accepted (async processing)\n- `redemptionId`: Reservation ID for tracking\n- `status`: \"processing\"\n- Email delivery happens in background"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "202 Accepted - Voucher Reserved",
          "originalRequest": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": ""
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/admin/redemptions/send-to-user",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "admin",
                "redemptions",
                "send-to-user"
              ]
            }
          },
          "status": "Accepted",
          "code": 202,
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Voucher is being sent via email\",\n  \"redemptionId\": \"cl123456789abcdefghijklm\",\n  \"userId\": \"clh1234567890abcdefghijk\",\n  \"email\": \"user@company.com\",\n  \"prizeId\": \"clh9876543210zyxwvutsrqp\",\n  \"customAmount\": 50.00,\n  \"status\": \"processing\",\n  \"notes\": \"Voucher email is being sent. Check status later for completion.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin - Bulk Redeem Vouchers",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{auth_token}}",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"prizeId\": \"clh9876543210zyxwvutsrqp\",\n  \"customAmount\": 50.00,\n  \"campaignId\": \"optional-campaign-id\",\n  \"users\": [\n    {\n      \"userId\": \"clh1111111111111111111111\",\n      \"email\": \"user1@company.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"userId\": \"clh2222222222222222222222\",\n      \"email\": \"user2@company.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"userId\": \"clh3333333333333333333333\",\n      \"email\": \"user3@company.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/admin/redemptions/bulk-redeem",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "admin",
            "redemptions",
            "bulk-redeem"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Send vouchers to multiple users (up to 100) via email\n\n**Required Permissions**: `vouchers:send_to_users`\n\n**Request Body**:\n- `prizeId` (string): Single CUID for all vouchers\n- `customAmount` (number): Same amount for all users (must be within voucher range)\n- `campaignId` (string, optional): Tremendous campaign template ID\n- `users` (array): Array of {userId, email} objects (1-100 items)\n  - Each email must match the user's registered email\n\n**Response**: 207 Multi-Status\n- `summary`: Overall success/failure counts\n- `results`: Array with status for each user\n- Email delivery happens in background"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "207 Multi-Status - Bulk Initiated",
          "originalRequest": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": ""
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/admin/redemptions/bulk-redeem",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "admin",
                "redemptions",
                "bulk-redeem"
              ]
            }
          },
          "status": "Multi-Status",
          "code": 207,
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Bulk redemption initiated\",\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"total\": 3,\n    \"successful\": 3,\n    \"failed\": 0\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"userId\": \"clh1111111111111111111111\",\n      \"email\": \"user1@company.com\",\n      \"prizeId\": \"clh9876543210zyxwvutsrqp\",\n      \"success\": true,\n      \"redemptionId\": \"clr1111111111111111111111\",\n      \"voucherCode\": \"voucher-code-123\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"userId\": \"clh2222222222222222222222\",\n      \"email\": \"user2@company.com\",\n      \"prizeId\": \"clh9876543210zyxwvutsrqp\",\n      \"success\": true,\n      \"redemptionId\": \"clr2222222222222222222222\",\n      \"voucherCode\": \"voucher-code-456\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"userId\": \"clh3333333333333333333333\",\n      \"email\": \"user3@company.com\",\n      \"prizeId\": \"clh9876543210zyxwvutsrqp\",\n      \"success\": true,\n      \"redemptionId\": \"clr3333333333333333333333\",\n      \"voucherCode\": \"voucher-code-789\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "User - Redeem Prize",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
