        "description": "Cancel a redemption within 3 days of creation\n\n**Path Parameters**:\n- `id` (string): Redemption ID\n\n**Request Body**:\n- `reason` (string): Cancellation reason for audit trail\n\n**Response**: 200 OK with cancellation details\n- Refunds coins back to user's redeemable balance\n- Updates redemption status to \"cancelled\"\n\n**Possible Errors**:\n- 400: Cannot cancel shipped orders\n- 400: 3-day cancellation window expired"
      },
